      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JACK JACK (8) has a strong winning strike-rate here with two wins and a placing from four tries. Comes off a (17.38) win last time, scoring by 5 lengths in a Grade 4 over 324m at Richmond Straight. With a clean break looks hard to beat. BEST SURPRISE (2) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 0.8 lengths win at this track in a handy 22.32. Has a low draw and in form and has the ability. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Expecting another bold showing. ZIPPING MCKEON (1) last raced on January 5 when fourth (21.23) over 365m at Nowra in a Grade 5. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. UNREACHABLE (3) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to atone.",
